{"type":"message","id":"f6080eae","parentId":"c948667a","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:34:36.878Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Sí, lo volvió a coger mal porque otra vez quedó partido.\n\nCopia **esto exacto**, sin partir `docs`:\n\n```powershell\ngog auth add atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com --services gmail,calendar,drive,contacts,docs,sheets\n```\n\n### Truco\nNo lo escribas a mano.  \n**Cópialo y pégalo completo**.\n\nSi quieres evitar ese problema, prueba esta versión con comillas:\n\n```powershell\ngog auth add atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com --services \"gmail,calendar,drive,contacts,docs,sheets\"\n```\n\nUsa esa mejor.  \nCuando te responda, me pegas la salida.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fc121c358a0b3df0169c48d2c93c88191973811c4e4ba3d23\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":236,"output":152,"cacheRead":127104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127492,"cost":{"input":0.00059,"output":0.00228,"cacheRead":0.031776,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.034645999999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774488871994,"responseId":"resp_0fc121c358a0b3df0169c48d2b4f4c8191a6566d8ca654ac5b"}}
