{"type":"message","id":"c92b8411","parentId":"25790bf6","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:35:06.004Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Estás pegando **el comando viejo roto** otra vez.\n\nPega **este**, exacto, con comillas:\n\n```powershell\ngog auth add atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com --services \"gmail,calendar,drive,contacts,docs,sheets\"\n```\n\nLa clave es que diga:\n\n- `docs`\n- no `do cs`\n\nSi quieres, incluso mejor copia solo esta línea de abajo:\n\n`gog auth add atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com --services \"gmail,calendar,drive,contacts,docs,sheets\"`\n\nPégame luego la respuesta exacta.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fc121c358a0b3df0169c48d4a0c5c81918ec19f0563025f0e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":302,"output":130,"cacheRead":127360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127792,"cost":{"input":0.000755,"output":0.0019500000000000001,"cacheRead":0.03184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.034545}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774488896626,"responseId":"resp_0fc121c358a0b3df0169c48d44470c8191883db09bc8fc71e5"}}
